# ── Test fixtures that are LOCAL real recordings ────────────────────────────
# These are captures from THIS machine's real cc/codex/GLM sessions (and the
# live GLM quota probe) — they carry personal usage/session data, not shared
# test inputs, so they stay local. Shared protocol/benchmark fixtures in
# tests/codex_host|cc_host|memory/fixtures (model-list, schema-baseline,
# eval-queries.yaml, …) are NOT ignored — tests depend on them.
tests/quota/fixtures/
tests/model_os/fixtures/
# real cc init recording — carries local /Users/<home> paths (PII):
tests/fixtures/cc-init-291.json

